      "width": 240,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "① Identity defines behavior\n   (SOUL.md = system prompt)\n\n② Skills constrain actions\n   (runbooks, not freestyle)\n\n③ MCP = pluggable tools\n   (swap without rewrite)\n\n④ GAIT = trust through\n   auditability",
